&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;I consider this type of data &lt;em&gt;reference&lt;/em&gt; data, as it’s not created by myself. So to distinguish it from other notes in my Obsidian vault, surprisingly enough, I keep it in a folder at the root of my vault called &lt;em&gt;references&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
