&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=bradlc.vscode-tailwindcss" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Tailwind CSS IntelliSense&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
