&lt;p&gt;I plan on publishing each chapter of the course on this page as I write it. If you would like to receive a copy of each chapter in your inbox when it goes live, then please &lt;a href="https://practicalhugo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;sign up for course content by email&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
