&lt;h2 id="scalability"&gt;Scalability&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Does it scale?&lt;/strong&gt; We&amp;rsquo;re not talking about front end frameworks here (let&amp;rsquo;s leave that for another one). Instead, we&amp;rsquo;re trying to solve the problem you have when you need to add in an extra step (or stage) to a flow you created last week, let&amp;rsquo;s say.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Does your system allow you to add in extra Artboards — anywhere in the sequence&lt;/strong&gt; — without you having to go through and rename the rest of your Artboards to maintain some sort of order?&lt;/p&gt;
